result.notes:
Alieia VRE supports the performance evaluation, benchmarking and decision making process of Alieia, a Greek aquafarming company, to improve its profitability and minimise environmental impacts. The VRE enables Alieia aquafarmers to:
- evaluate and optimise their performance in terms of production Key Performance Indicators (KPIs);
- carry out benchmarking analysis comparing their performance against best practices and the competition;
perform a techno economic investment analysis.
